    key=value [ansible]

variable "variable name" {
  type = <data type>
  default = "<default value>"
}

syntax
=========
variable "image_id" {
    type = string
    default = "ami-041e2ea9402c46c32"
    description = "RHEL ami-id"
  
}

how can we call variable in terraform file 
------------------------------------------
var.<variable name>

tagging strategy 
-----------------
when its created 
who created
which environment
